  Vcl.ExtCtrls, AdvPanel, NxCollection, Vcl.StdCtrls, Vcl.DBCtrls, DBAdvLe,
  Vcl.Grids, Vcl.DBGrids, CRGrid, AdvEdit, advlued, AdvGroupBox,
